#### Changes
- Greatclub loses two-handed property and gains heavy and versatile properties
- Handaxe loses thrown property, to avoid making it strictly better than the light hammer. Hatchet created as throwing axe option
- Blowgun changed to simple weapon, gains special property (can use Con in place of Dex for damage)
- Heavy crossbow changed to simple weapon

